Thank u dear mam for so much love..!!
.
At this moment, I want to take a moment to express my deepest gratitude to my dear PLUSH team. They have always gone the extra mile, working tirelessly, often beyond hours, without expectations—only with pure dedication. They have stood by me, serving and supporting our students at every step, never hesitating to start early or stay late.

What makes it even more special is that most of my PLUSH team were once my students. They truly understand the value of learning and growth, which is why they extend the same care and commitment to every student at PLUSH Academy. Month after month, they travel with me across different states and cities, ensuring that every aspiring artist gets the best experience possible.

I feel incredibly grateful and blessed to have such a passionate team. And to my dear students—your love and affection mean the world to me. Thank you for being a part of this journey and for trusting us with your dreams.

Loads of love to all my students from PLUSH Academy! ❤️
